Description: This is a stunning, new, heavily beaded fold-over clutch style hand bag from MOYNA in an argyle pattern in shades of pink, light blue, gold and dark green. Under the floldover section, you will find solid pink beads with the word "PREP" in dark green beads. It has a zippered opening tucked in the fold of the foldover section. It's lined with matching pink fabric and features an interior slip top pocket. MOYNA bags are sold on-line and in fine stores, like Anthropologie and Neiman Marcus. This NEW with tag evening bag originally retailed for $159. This particular preppy argyle style is a rare and delightful find. It will be shipped in it's dust bag to protect these stunning beads. About MOYNA SINGH - An intimate knowledge of Asian handicraft and personal experience with the design of home goods in India lead Moyna Singh to create her own eponymous line of accessories. Each piece embraces traditional beading techniques, with a careful selection of materials to complement the design. Case in point: preppy-inspired embellishment, and clever construction that hides a zipper in the fold of this glamorous clutch. *Please see the item specifics for the dimensions of this bag and use these dimensions to determine if the size will suit your needs.
